ass=\"bg-[#eef3ff] text-navy text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/en/blog/category/case-study\">Case Study</a><a class=\"bg-[#eef3ff] text-navy text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/en/blog/category/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"bg-[#eef3ff] text-navy text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/en/blog/category/webinar\">Webinar</a><a class=\"bg-[#eef3ff] text-navy text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/en/blog/category/guide\">Guide</a></div><div class=\"space-y-8\"><a class=\"block bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\" href=\"/en/blog/from-chaos-to-control\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">2025-11-10</span><span class=\"bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">Case Study</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">From Chaos to Control: Launching EN/ES Programs Across 11 Sites</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-3\">How a multi-site contractor deployed bilingual safety programs across 11 locations with SafetyLink.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->en-es</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->construction</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->compliance</span></div></a><a class=\"block bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\" href=\"/en/blog/5-policy-mistakes\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">2025-11-10</span><span class=\"bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">Guide</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">5 Policy Mistakes That Fail in Audits — and What to Do Instead</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-3\">Avoid common policy errors that trigger audit findings and learn how to build defensible documentation.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->policies</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->audit-ready</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->compliance</span></div></a><a class=\"block bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\" href=\"/en/blog/bilingual-training-that-works\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">2025-11-10</span><span class=\"bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">Blog</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Bilingual Training That Works: Scheduling, Tracking, Reinforcement</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-3\">Practical strategies for delivering effective bilingual safety training across diverse workforces.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->training</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->en-es</span></div></a><a class=\"block bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\" href=\"/en/blog/reducing-recordable-injuries\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">2025-11-10</span><span class=\"bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">Blog</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Reducing Recordable Injuries: A Site-Specific Approach for Contractors</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-3\">Site-specific safety approaches that measurably reduce recordable injuries in construction.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->injury-prevention</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->construction</span></div></a><a class=\"block bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\" href=\"/en/blog/lockout-tagout-implementation\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">2025-11-10</span><span class=\"bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">Guide</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Lockout/Tagout Implementation Guide: From Policy to Practice</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-3\">A step-by-step guide to implementing effective LOTO programs that pass audits and protect workers.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->loto</span><span class=\"text-xs text-[#686868]\">#<!-- -->training</span></div></a></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10\"><div><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-1.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-8 w-auto mb-4\"/><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4\">The only legally defensible safety compliance platform backed by OSHA leadership and top labor law experts. Protecting workforces with bilingual training, audits, and compliance solutions.</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 italic\">SafetyLink is not affiliated with or endorsed by OSHA. Advisory support provided by former OSHA leadership.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/solutions\">Solutions</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/services\">Services</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Contact</a></li><li><a cl